<STRONG>1996 National Conference of Texas Schedule</STRONG></CENTER>
<P>from <I>1996 National Conference of Texas Program<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
</I><STRONG>SATURDAY, OCTOBER 26</STRONG><BR>
7:30 a.m. - 6:00 p.m. -- Registration -- Exhibit Hall 2/3<BR>
9:00 a.m. - 10:15 a.m. -- Concurrent Sessions (Set I) -- (See &quot;Sessions
Online&quot; for descriptions & locations)<BR>
9:00 a.m. - 6:00 p.m. -- Tech Labs Open -- Rotunda Area<BR>
10:00 a.m. - 6:00 p.m. -- Exhibits Open -- Exhibit Hall 2/3<BR>
10:30 a.m. - 11:45 a.m. -- Concurrent Sessions (Set II) -- (See &quot;Sessions
Online&quot; for descriptions & locations)<BR>
11:45 a.m. - 12:15 p.m. -- Facilitator Meeting -- Lone Star<BR>
11:45 a.m. - 1:30 p.m. -- Visit Exhibits/TeamTime/Concessions -- Exhibit
Hall 2/3<BR>
1:00 p.m. - 3:00 p.m. -- Opening General Session/Pre-Session Entertainment
-- Exhibit Hall 1<BR>
3:00 p.m. - 3:30 p.m. -- Visit Exhibits/Concessions -- Exhibit Hall 2/3<BR>
3:30 p.m. - 5:00 p.m. -- Concurrent Sessions (Set III) -- (See &quot;Sessions
Online&quot; for descriptions & locations)<BR>
5:00 p.m. - 6:00 p.m. -- Visit Exhibits/Concessions -- Exhibit Hall 2/3<BR>
<BR>
<STRONG>SUNDAY, OCTOBER 27</STRONG><BR>
8:00 a.m. - 2:00 p.m. -- Registration -- Exhibit Hall 2/3<BR>
