<blockquote>

<font size=+3>W</font>elcome to Genentech's Investor Relations department.  Our role is to provide accurate and updated information about the scientific progress and financial status of Genentech to the investment community.
<p>
In this section you can view the most recent Annual Report, Quarterly Report and Quarterly Corporate Summary, as well as a Historical Financial Summary .  You can also find details of our various Strategic Alliances.  
<p>
<UL>
<li> <a href=extstock/GNE.NYSE.html>Genentech Stock Quote</a>
<li> <a href=Q3/index.html#business>Business Updates</a>
<LI> <a href=financial_summary.html>Historical Financial Summary</a>
