<LI> <a href=forms.html>Forms 10K & 10Q</a>
<LI> <A HREF = "corporate_summary.html#alliances">Strategic Alliances</A>
<LI> <a href=../../pressrelease/>Genentech Press Releases</a>
</UL>
<p>
We welcome your suggestions and comments.  Security analysts and representatives of portfolio management firms may contact Susan Bentley, Director, Investor Relations.  Telephone (415) 225-1034, Fax (415) 225-8326, <A HREF=mailto:investor.relations@gene.com>Investor.Relations@gene.com</a>.

<h2>Stockholder Inquiries</h2>  

Communication concerning transfer requirements, lost certificates and change of address should be directed to Genentech's transfer agent:
<p>
Boston EquiServe<br>
Stockholder Services Division<br>
Post Office Box 644<br>
M/S 45-02-09<br>
Boston, MA  02102-0644<br>
Telephone:  617-575-3400
<p>
If you need additional assistance or information regarding the company, contact the Investor Relations Department at Genentech's corporate offices at (415) 225-1599 or (415) 225-1260, or send an Email to: <A HREF=mailto:investor.relations@gene.com>Investor.Relations@gene.com</a>.

<h2>Still Curious?</h2>

Discover the art of science at Genentech in <A HREF=../Science>Science Science Science</A>, or visit the <A HREF=../Pipeline/>Product Pipeline</A> to see what Genentech scientists are working on for the future.  <A HREF=../Company/>About Genentech</A> will fill you in on the company and people behind our <A HREF=../Medicines/>Medicines</A>.  Learn about the basic principles of the life sciences at Genentech in <A HREF=../Company/Responsibility/about_ae.html>Access Excellence</A>, our national online educational program for biology teachers.   All this may make you want to visit the <A HREF=../Career/>Career Sphere</A>.  Have fun, learn a lot, and help yourself to a <A HREF=/local-bin/bites.cgi>Bite of Biotech</A> before you leave.
