<H1>Genentech Quarterly News<br>Third Quarter 1996</H1>

<img src="gne_3_logo.gif">

<br>
<blockquote>


<table border=5>

<tr>
<td><center><i><font size=+2 color=brown><br>In this Issue</font></i></center>
