<html><head><title>Science, Science, Science</title></head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">


<!-- begin-gne-header -->
<a href=/cgi-bin/imagemap/banner>
<img border=0 src=../banner.gif alt=Science ismap></a>
<!-- end-gne-header -->
<p>
<center>
<a href=/cgi-bin/imagemap/science_map>
<img border=0 src=science_map.gif alt=Science, Science, Science ismap></a>
</center>
<p>
<blockquote>
<FONT SIZE=+3>S</FONT>cience at Genentech is a complicated, interdependent dance of minds and molecules and machinery and business and imagination and compassion.  It is the foundation of Genentech's success.
<p>
Start here to explore the different areas of science, their roles, and what it's like to be a scientist at Genentech.  Learn how various groups integrate their skills to create the swiftest voyage in the industry of medicines from discovery to market.
<p>
<UL>
<LI> <a href=discovery.html>Discovery Research</a>
<LI> <a href=clinical.html>Clinical Development</a>
<LI> <a href=process.html>Process Science</a>
<LI> <a href=manufacturing.html>Quality Manufacturing</a>
<LI> <a href=scientific_policy.html>Being a Scientist at Genentech</a>
<li> <a href=/rmat-bin/entry.cgi>Collaborative Research Materials Program</a>
<li> <a href=../Company/achievement.html>Genentech Scientific Achievements</a>
</UL>
<p>
Discovery Research, Clinical Development and Process Science all contribute to the development of a new medicine.  Each area performs specific tasks that the other areas count on. Making medicine requires a sustained contribution from all groups right up to the final manufacturing process, where scientists from each area collaborate with Quality Manufacturing to assure that ample amount of pure product is made to meet the needs of clinical testing and, ultimately, the market.
<p>
<h2>Still Curious?</h2>
<p>
Learn more about the basic principles of the life sciences in <A HREF=../Company/Responsibility/about_ae.html>Access Excellence</A>, our national online educational program.  There you will find science news, history, a glossary of terms and many other resources. Genentech built the site to assist high-school biology teachers in teaching biology.  But whether you are a teacher or not, go ahead and help yourself to this treasure of information and resources.
<p>
You may also want visit the <A HREF=../Pipeline/>Product Pipeline</A> to see what Genentech scientists are working on for the future, or <A HREF=../Company/>About Genentech</A> which will fill you in on the company and people behind our <A HREF=../Medicines/>Medicines</A>,  or get the corporate bottomline in <A HREF=../Investor/>Investor Relations</A>.  All this may make you want to visit the <A HREF=../Career/>Career Sphere</A>.  Have fun, learn a lot, and take a <A HREF=/local-bin/bites.cgi>Bite of Biotech</A> before you leave.
<p>
</blockquote>
