Learn more about the life sciences in <A HREF=../Company/Responsibility/about_ae.html>Access Excellence</A>, our national online educational program for high school biology teachers.  <A HREF=../Company/>About Genentech</A> will fill you in on the company and people behind our <A HREF=../Medicines>Medicines</A>, and a visit to the <A HREF=../Pipeline/>Product Pipeline</A> will reveal what Genentech scientists are working on for the future.   Take some time to discover the art of science at Genentech in <A HREF=../Science/>Science Science Science</A>.  All this may make you want to visit the Genentech <A HREF=../Career/>Career Sphere</A>.  Have fun, learn a lot, and have <A HREF=/local-bin/bites.cgi>Bite of Biotech</A> for the road.


