<p>
<h2>Tips for Searching</h2>

You may search for a whole or a part of a word.  For example, enter "lab" to find documents that contain the word "laboratory."
<p>
The search is case in-sensitive; your keyword will match both upper- or lowercase words in the documents.
<p>
You may also search for multiple words at once, divided by a space.  For example, you might enter "recombinant&nbsp;dna" to find documents that combine the two topics.
