<p>
<blockquote>
<font size=+3>E</font>leven of the approved products of biotechnology stem from Genentech science. Genentech manufactures and markets six of these protein-based pharmaceuticals listed below one of which is available in two formulations. The other five are licensed to other companies.
<p>
<ul>
<li><A HREF=activase.html>Activase</a><sup><font size=-1>&reg</font></sup> (Alteplase, recombinant), a tissue-plasminogen activator, - For treatment of heart attack, acute ischemic stroke and acute massive pulmonary embolism.
<p>
<li><a href=protropin.html>Protropin</a><sup><font size=-1>&reg</font></sup> (somatrem for injection) growth hormone - For treatment of growth hormone deficiency (GHD) in children.
<p>
<li><a href=nutropin.html>Nutropin</a><sup><font size=-1>&reg</font></sup> [somatropin (rDNA origin) for injection] human growth hormone - For treatment of GHD and growth failure associated with chronic renal insufficiency (CRI) prior to kidney transplantation, and short stature associated with Turner syndrome.
<p>
<li><a href=nutropin_aq.html>Nutropin AQ<img border=0 src="tm.gif"></a> [somatropin (rDNA origin) injection] a liquid formulation of growth hormone - For treatment of GHD in children and growth failure due to CRI prior to kidney transplantation.
<p>
<li><a href=pulmozyme.html>Pulmozyme</a><sup><font size=-1>&reg</font></sup> (dornase alfa) Inhalation Solution -  For management of cystic fibrosis.	
<p>
<li><A HREF=actimmune.html>Actimmune</A><sup><font size=-1>&reg</font></sup> (Interferon gamma-1b) - To manage chronic granulomatous disease (CGD), a rare, inherited immune disorder.
</ul>
<p>


Through its long-standing <AHREF = "assistance">Patient Assistance Program</A>, Genentech assures that everyone who needs these important medicines can get them.  Genentech also supports the continuing improvement of patient care through its post-marketing studies, which collect data on the health progress of patients who use Genentech medicines nationwide.
<p>
Learn more about Genentech's products by exploring the links listed above.  <!--If you need more information about any of the products, please send an email message to ????? [LINK]-->  

