<LI>Rosenbloom J, Feldman G, Freundlich B, Jimenez SA:  Inhibition of Excessive Scleroderma Fibroblast Collagen Production by Recombinant Gamma-interferon.  <I>Arth Rheum 29</I>:851-856, 1986.<P>

