<center><h1>Genentech, Inc.</h1></center>
<center><h3>Job Posting</h3></center>
<hr>
<pre>
Position:         Administrative Assistant
Requisition #:    96-0000979

</pre>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Description</strong><br>
Primary responsibility is to provide administrative support to the two Directors of Biochemical Manufacturing.  Additionally, provide support to various people within manufacturing on an as needed basis.  Responsibilities include: maintaining the supplies in the canteen and copy room, update two conference room calendars, take meeting minutes, distribute department mail, and arrange for maintenance of office area.  Organize department meetings, off-sites, and parties; prepare and assemble yearly Biochemical Manufacturing Handbook, and creation and maintenance of various databases.  Assist Directors in budgeting, preparing presentations, and expense reports.  Provide computer hardware and software support.  Act as the site manager in emergency situations.  Responsible for additional projects as requested.
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Requirements</strong><br>
Knowledge of Macintosh with proficiency in Word 6.0, FileMaker Proand presentation software.  A strong understanding of Excel is a plus.  Excellent organizational skills and project management.  Effectively communicate (written and verbal) with people at various levels.  Experienced in drafting routine correspondence, formatting slides, and setting up simple databases and spreadsheets.  Self-starter with the ability to make decisions with little guidance.
<p>
<hr><em>
Send resume to <a href=mailto:jobs@gene.com>jobs@gene.com</a></em>

