<pre>
Position:         Facility Services Associate Director/Director - Vacaville
Requisition #:    96-0000916

</pre>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Description</strong><br>
Reporting to the General Manager, the leader of the Facility Services group will have responsibility for maintenance and calibration of process, analytical and utility equipment, buildings and grounds, site and employee security and telecommunications at Genentech's newly constructed pharmaceutical production plant at Vacaville. Operation of site utilities is also part of this function.Initially the location will be in South San Francisco until the plant is ready for start-up which is expected to be by mid-to-late 1997. The job will involve partnering with project engineering, validation, manufacturing and quality assurance teams throughout the construction, start-up and validation phases and also staffing and developing the facility group in order to support bringing manufacturing on line in the 1998-1999 time frame. 
<p>
