<center><h1>Genentech, Inc.</h1></center>
<center><h3>Job Posting</h3></center>
<hr>
<pre>
Position:         Scientist
Requisition #:    96-0001006

</pre>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Description</strong><br>
You will monitor existing commercial, large-scale recovery or purification processes, as well as identify/correct problems.  You will also collaborate with other Scientists and Process Engineers on yield improvement, plant improvement, and new facilities.
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Requirements</strong><br>
Ph.D. or equivalent in biochemistry, bioanalytical chemistry, or similar area.  A conceptual understanding of chromatography and protein characterization is essential.  Having initiative, a sense of perspective, effective interpersonal skills and the ability to adapt quickly to change are also essential.
<p>
<hr><em>
