<center><h1>Genentech, Inc.</h1></center>
<center><h3>Job Posting</h3></center>
<hr>
<pre>
Position:         Systems Analyst
Requisition #:    96-0001050

</pre>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Description</strong><br>
Responsible for directing and participation in the analysis, design, evaluation, testing, documentation and implementation of computer systems.  Responsible for the technical design of systems integration software.  Plans and directs studies of potential applications and prepares design proposals to reflect costs, time and alternative actions.  Conducts analysis of systems specifications and develops block diagrams and flowcharts.  Develops cost analysis and justifications of data processing systems.  Develops conversion and system implementation plans.  Prepares and obtains approval of systems and programming documentation. Recommends changes in development, maintenance and system standards.
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Requirements</strong><br>
MS in relevant field with 3 years of applicable experience, BS in relevant field with 5 years of applicable experience, or 9 years of applicable experience.  Knowledge of UNIX and ORACLE.  Good communication skills.  Experienced at working in a team environment.  Knowledge of POMS, BPCS, NovaManage, or Beckman LIMS a plus.
