<pre>
Position:         Unit Supervisor - Fermentation
Requisition #:    96-0000944

</pre>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Description</strong><br>
Coordination of all department activities with the Unit Supervisor of the day and grave shifts and the Technical Services Unit Supervisor.  Final review and approval of all department production documentation. Ensure maintenance of pertinent records, documentation and systems.  Assure that work in the area is performed by appropriately trained personnel in compliance with applicable GMP and safety standards.  Interact with other departments such as QA, QC, Process Sciences, Manufacturing Sciences, Recovery Operations, and Regulatory Affairs.
