BA/BS in Life Sciences.  Minimum of 6 years experience and accomplishment in biotechnology with at least 2 years of manufacturing background.  Minimum of 2-3 years supervisory experience.  Strong technical background and a working knowledge of fermentation equipment. FDA and Quality requirements for bulk manufacturing.  Knowledge of shift operations and strong organizational and interpersonal skills.  Demonstrated leadership capabilities.
