<blockquote>
<center><h1>Genentech, Inc.</h1></center>
<center><h3>Job Posting</h3></center>
<hr>
<pre>
Position:         Validation Specialist
Requisition #:    96-0001059

</pre>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Description</strong><br>
To provide validation support for new and existing computerized systems within the Operations Systems Department.  Will evaluate validation status of computerized systems.  Develop complete and thorough documentation to support validated status.  Participate in development and execution of validation testing for Operations computerized systems.  Evaluate changes to computerized systems for impact on validation status.  Plan and execute work necessary to maintain validated status of systems undergoing change or revision.
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Requirements</strong><br>
Undergraduate degree in science related field.  3-5 years experience in pharmaceutical industry.  Knowledge and experience in the areas of validation principles, regulatory expectations of computerized systems, and industry practices related to computer validation.  Knowledge of cGMPs, GLPs and other regulatory requirements applicable to computer validation.  Knowledge of manufacturing, quality, and related supporting activities.  Strong technical documentation, problem solving/analytical, and communication skills.
<p>
<hr><em>
Send resume to <a href=mailto:jobs@gene.com>jobs@gene.com</a></em>

