Position:         Administrative Assistant
Requisition #:    96-0000995

</pre>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Description</strong><br>
This position will provide administrative support to the Employment Manager and the Employment Representatives. Duties include preparing correspondence, spreadsheets, reports, contracts and other employment department communications; scheduling, organizing, arranging and attending meetings and other business activities.  Preparing presentation materials including slides, agendas and meeting packages; serving as a resource at Genentech for information related to the Employment Department.  Communicates with executive, administrative and other internal and external parties to gather or convey information for the employment manager.
<p>
