<p>
<strong>Requirements</strong><br>
Minimum 5 years related administrative assistant experience.  Must be proficient with PC systems including MS Word and Excel for windows.  Proficiency with presentation software preferred.  Must have excellent clerical, composition and grammar skills.  Must be able to effectively interact with a variety of personalities and professional levels.  Must have demonstrated the ability to work independently and proactively.  Exposure to sensitive and confidential information will require considerable use of tact, diplomacy, discretion and judgment.
