<blockquote>
<center><h1>Genentech, Inc.</h1></center>
<center><h3>Job Posting</h3></center>
<hr>
<pre>
Position:         Manager - Product Reimbursement
Requisition #:    96-0000939

</pre>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Description</strong><br>
Monitor health care policy, coverage and payment trends.  Analyze the impact on customers and existing product lines.  With core team input, develop response strategies to counter or minimize impact on present or future sales.
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Requirements</strong><br>
Must be an expert in the government health care legislative process, the regulatory bodies that monitor the program?s health care policy development, and the administrative structure of the funding sources.  Excellent communicator who is able to establish and maintain good relationships with critical decision makers.  Skilled project manager who has experience managing multiple responsibilities, legislative events and team member interfaces within established timelines.  Team player who can responsibly delegate to other team members when necessary.Effective communicator who can work well and communicate effectively with a broad cross-section of disciplines.  Knowledgeable in the product, disease state, and the disease state continuum.  Proficient strategist to develop direction for products in response to investigative and analytical research.
<p>
<hr><em>
Send resume to <a href=mailto:jobs@gene.com>jobs@gene.com</a></em>

</blockquote>
