<blockquote>
<center><h1>Genentech, Inc.</h1></center>
<center><h3>Job Posting</h3></center>
<hr>
<pre>
Position:         Reimbursement Supervisor
Requisition #:    96-0000941

</pre>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Description</strong><br>
This individual is responsible for the daily operations of the Reimbursement Hotline and Genentech Assistance Programs.  Their goal is to improve and maintain the day to day efficiency in the delivery of the Genentech programs or reimbursement services to both internal clients and external customers.
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Requirements</strong><br>
Degree in the health sciences or at least 3 years job experience in the Health Reimbursement field.  The individual must be proficient in the basics of reimbursement billing, benefit identification, and appeal development.  This position requires excellent analytical and investigational skills in addition to the ability to communicate effectively both verbally and in a written format.  This individual must demonstrate a basic understanding and use of data bases, spreadsheets, and word processing.  The individual must have a demonstrated ability as a team leader, having worked to enhance a team result by fostering good intergroup relationships.
<p>
<hr><em>
Send resume to <a href=mailto:jobs@gene.com>jobs@gene.com</a></em>

</blockquote>
