<center><h1>Genentech, Inc.</h1></center>
<center><h3>Job Posting</h3></center>
<hr>
<pre>
Position:         Security Supervisor
Requisition #:    96-0001045

</pre>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Description</strong><br>
Supervise and train security personnel to ensure effective responses to security, facility, emergency and disaster response team training and responses.  Maintain and update procedures to ensure an effective security and safety program in accordance with company policies and guidelines.  Operate and supervise others responsible for operating state of the art security and facilities computer systems providing effective response to security, facility and emergency response incidents.
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Requirements</strong><br>
Minimum 5 years security experience with at least one year supervisory experience.  Valid California driver's license with clean DMV record.  Knowledge of security and facility operations, particularly in the industrial and high technology fields.  Basic emergency response skills in the areas of chemical releases, medical emergencies and fire responses.  Basic working knowledge of basic security access control, cctv and fire systems.
