Position:         Senior Network Specialist
Requisition #:    97-0000048

</pre>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Description</strong><br>
This position is responsible for providing technical leadership and support for the corporate data networks, including developing requirements, evaluation, design and implementation for new technology that supports business requirements.  In-depth technical knowledge is required in a variety of network technologies and architectures.  Works closely with other I.R. professionals in problem determination and resolution.  Ability to communicate at all levels within the company.
