<blockquote>
<center><h1>Genentech, Inc.</h1></center>
<center><h3>Job Posting</h3></center>
<hr>
<pre>
Position:         Senior Programmer/Analyst
Requisition #:    96-0000772

</pre>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Description</strong><br>
To develop system specifications, design systems, program, document, debug and assist with implementation of new systems and modifications to existing systems.  Work performed will include providing programming and system design support.  Evaluate alternative approaches to solving problems either by using existing systems or other sources.  Provide technical support in computer-related areas, such as selection of equipment or software.  Monitor system usage in order to analyze performance, desirable enhancements and resource requirements.
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Requirements</strong><br>
BS/BA desirable.  MS or MBA is a plus. 3-5 years programming experience in the primary language which will be used; language will vary for different programmers within the group.  5+ years data processing experience is required.  Strong background in the hardware environment that will be used (DEC VAX, PC's) is required.  Experience with systems analysis and design.  Experience with user interactions, communications, training.  Ability to rapidly program and deliver quality systems.  Specific training in programming techniques, database, systems analysis is a plus.
<p>
<hr><em>
Send resume to <a href=mailto:jobs@gene.com>jobs@gene.com</a></em>

