<blockquote>
<center><h1>Genentech, Inc.</h1></center>
<center><h3>Job Posting</h3></center>
<hr>
<pre>
Position:         Contract Coordinator III
Requisition #:    96-0000954

</pre>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Description</strong><br>
To provide support to Medical Affairs by facilitating the contract negotiation process between Genentech and its clinical researchers.  In this position, the Coordinator will be responsible for timely and accurate processing and follow-up on contract requests, maintenance of a contract database and development of all necessary non-standard contract arrangements.  The Coordinator will work closely with other members of the Medical Affairs financial staff in monitoring contract payments, commitments and budgets.  The Coordinator will work closely with Genentech?s legal department for final contract approval, ensuring that requests form investigators and consultants for variance from standard language are in Genentech's best interests.
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Requirements</strong><br>
BS/BA in a Life Science, pharmaceutical industry experience and contract experience are preferred.  Financial analysis/accounting skills are desirable.  Excellent communication skills and attention to detail.  Proficiency with Macintosh computers, specifically with MS Word and FileMaker Pro.  Familiarity with contract basics and structure.  Individual should be self-motivated and able to work under tight time constraints.
<p>
<hr><em>
Send resume to <a href=mailto:jobs@gene.com>jobs@gene.com</a></em>

</blockquote>
