<strong>Description</strong><br>
Key leadership position in accounting operations for accounts payable and fixed assets. Pprovide a vision of and lead the department towards strategies and tactics that will streamline processes to ensure short cycle time, high quality of service to customers and accurate reporting.  Will be very involved in the design and implementation of new financial systems.  Must be innovative and be able to continue the movement to be 'best of class' for both accounts payable and fixed assets.
