Position:         System Analyst
Requisition #:    96-0000967

</pre>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Description</strong><br>
Assist with implementation of new financial software with emphasis on the General Ledger, Financial Reporting, and Project Tracking modules.  Coordinate the monthly financial close process on the new system as well as the current system, which is to be replaced within the next year.  This position plays a key role in the monthly financial close process and reports to, and is backup for the Financial Systems Analyst.  Maintain financial reports and provide assistance in setting up on-line information access and various other requests.  Be responsible for upgrades, maintenance and coordination with Information Resources.  Assist users as necessary.
