<center><h1>Genentech, Inc.</h1></center>
<center><h3>Job Posting</h3></center>
<hr>
<pre>
Position:         Administrative Assistant
Requisition #:    96-0001049

</pre>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Description</strong><br>
This person will function as an Administrative Assistant to three (3) Associate Product Managers on a busy cardiovascular marketing team.  Responsible for a wide range of administrative duties including maintaining three (3) very busy calendars, setting up a variety of meetings and other business activities, making travel arrangements and working on special projects as assigned.  Generous amounts of typing, preparation and proofreading of correspondence.  Assemble and arrange for sales force mailings on a weekly basis.  Assistance and eventual responsibility for financials including purchase orders and invoices.
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Requirements</strong><br>
Must be proficient with Macintosh including Word and Powerpoint.  Excel and Filemaker Pro a plus.  Familiarity with Meeting Maker and Zmail also a plus.  Excellent organizational and project management skills.  Outstanding communication skills (written and verbal).  Ability to work in a fast paced,, results oriented department.  Must have excellent clerical, composition and grammar skills.  Must be able to effectively have the ability to prioritize and organize a large workflow and follow a project through to completion.  Must have demonstrated the ability to work independently and proactively and under deadline.
<p>
<hr><em>
Send resume to <a href=mailto:jobs@gene.com>jobs@gene.com</a></em>

