<blockquote>
<center><h1>Genentech, Inc.</h1></center>
<center><h3>Job Posting</h3></center>
<hr>
<pre>
Position:         Senior Product Manager - Cardiovascular
Requisition #:    97-0000001

</pre>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Description</strong><br>
The Senior Product Manager position in the New Products Marketing group will be responsible for (Therapeutic Area) New Products from IND through the end of Phase III.  This includes: developing the overall product marketing strategy; developing/implementing the pre-marketing plan; representing Marketing on the Project Core Team and/or Global Project Team; developing a strong partnership with other (Therapeutic Areas) Marketing personnel; developing and validating the long range forecast; and managing the promotional budget and 1 Product Manager.
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Requirements</strong><br>
BS/BA, preferably in one of the Life Sciences; MBA and/or related advanced degree desirable.  5+ years industry experience in a pharmaceutical and/or biotechnology company with 3+ years Product Management experience with related experience in Sales, Sales Training, Market Research, and/or New Product Planning.  This experience must include ethical therapeutic products, management of at least one Sales or Marketing professional, 1+ years as a Product Manager and responsibility for forecasting long range revenues (marketed and/or new product).  Evidence of recognized leadership as demonstrated by successful leadership role on task force/team.  Demonstrated creativity and flexibility by identifying new solutions to business problems.  Evidence of good quantitative analytical skills.  A strong understanding and meeting of customer needs.  Effective communication and conflict resolution skills.
<p>
<hr><em>
Send resume to <a href=mailto:jobs@gene.com>jobs@gene.com</a></em>

</blockquote>
