<pre>
Position:         Senior Regulatory Affairs Associate
Requisition #:    96-0000923

</pre>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Description</strong><br>
Responsible for developing, implementing, and conducting clinical compliance auditing, education, and communication assignments and projects to assess/assure the quality and integrity of clinical research data and documentation included in Genentech FDA submissions.
