Position:         Scientist
Requisition #:    96-0000882

</pre>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Description</strong><br>
We need an outstanding, highly motivated synthetic chemist to join our innovative program in drug discovery and development.  We seek a dedicated experimentalist with a proven record of achievement in organic synthesis, and a desire to become part of a multi-disciplinary team focused on drug targets in immunology, oncology, and cardiovascular disease.
