<blockquote>
<center><h1>Genentech, Inc.</h1></center>
<center><h3>Job Posting</h3></center>
<hr>
<pre>
Position:         Manager
Requisition #:    96-0000876

</pre>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Description</strong><br>
Manage a Manufacturing Quality Assurance (MQA) group with responsibility for product quality assurance of clinical and marketed processes at Genentech.  Responsibilities include Quality Assurance overview of manufacturing biochemical operations to ensure compliance, personnel management, systems (including the clinical documentation system), and product issues.  Developing and maintaining partnership with Manufacturing to continually improve product quality, and managing staff by providing appropriate opportunities for career development and timely performance feedback.
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Requirements</strong><br>
BS/BA/MS in Science, or equivalent with 7 to 10 years experience with Quality systems, and a good knowledge of biotech manufacturing processes, batch review and product release in the biotech pharmaceutical industry.  Previous management experience of 3 to 5 years required.
<p>
<hr><em>
Send resume to <a href=mailto:jobs@gene.com>jobs@gene.com</a></em>

