<center><h1>Genentech, Inc.</h1></center>
<center><h3>Job Posting</h3></center>
<hr>
<pre>
Position:         QA Supervisor
Requisition #:    96-0001023

</pre>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Description</strong><br>
Supervises and administers the QA Clinical Labeling system to ensure that Genentech Clinical Labeling can be accomplished with cGMPs and internal standards.  Oversees the creation, revision and control of all blind and open labeling to support clinical trials.  Accomplishes the above by directing the activities of the Clinical Labeling Compliance department.
<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Requirements</strong><br>
Bachelors degree in a relevant technical discipline and/or equivalent work experience.  Minimum 5 years experience with clinical labeling in the pharmaceutical industry or related field, preferably in quality control/assurance or regulatory affairs environment.  Previous supervisory experience required.  Experience with in-house labeling systems a plus.  Must have good written, verbal and interpersonal skills.  Must possess ability to lead technical and non-technical personnel.  Have thorough knowledge of cGMPs and their application to drug and biologic products.
<p>
<hr><em>
