<BLOCKQUOTE>

<CENTER>
<h1>Full Prescribing Information</h1>
<table><tr><td valign=top><UL><LI><A HREF="#description"> DESCRIPTION OF NUTROPIN AQ<img border=0 src="tm.gif"></a> 
<LI><A HREF="#pharmacology"> CLINICAL PHARMACOLOGY</a> 
