<strong>Description</strong><br>
Under the supervision of the Validation Manager, the Validation Specialist is responsible for: writing protocols and reports; performing testing, sample collection, data analysis, coordinating support resources, and preparation of test equipment.  The normal job functions will allow the Validation Specialist to interface with multiple departments across Genentech.  As required, the Validation Specialist may participate on project teams, review document and equipment change requests relating to validated systems (DCRs, ECRs) and review reports and data tables generated by peers.
