BA/BS in technical field.  Minimum 2 years pharmaceutical or biotech experience.  Familiarity with cGMPs.  Mechanical aptitude and computer literate.  Familiarity with Macintosh strongly desired.  Good problem solving skills, technical writing experience, and good interpersonal skills.  Ability to effectively manage own work schedule and balance multiple concurrent projects.
