<p>
<p>
<p>
<strong>Requirements</strong><br>
BS/BA or equivalent in scientific, medical or business field. 2-3 years experience in pharmaceuticalor medical related sales, in a hospital environment.  Position is in Orlando, FL.   Qualified candidates may contact Marcy Sullivan at (415) 586-0724 or fax to (415) 584-1523.  
