     <a href="ftp://ftp.hep.net/newsletters/aipfyi/latest.txt">
     <i>FYI  </i></a>  - policy newsletter
<br>
     (previous issues: 
     <a href="ftp://ftp.hep.net/newsletters/aipfyi/1995"> 1995 </a> and
     <a href="ftp://ftp.hep.net/newsletters/aipfyi/1994"> 1994 </a>)

