</ul>

<p>

Physics and Public Policy:
<ul>
<li>
The DOE <a href="http://www.ohre.doe.gov/">
Office of Human Radiation Experiments </a>
now has a web site with archives of declassified documents
of interest.
NPR reports on <A HREF="/rafiles/npr/nc062301-8.ram">
the federal task force investigating Cold War-era
radiation experiments and ethics</a> which is finishing its work.
(This is in <a href="http://www.realaudio.com/">
RealAudio</a> 10kbps format.  Players are available free.)
<li> The APS <a href="http://www.calpoly.edu/~dhafemei/publication.html">
statement and report on 60Hz EMF health effects</a>
are available.
</ul>
<p>
