Theory Group
</H1>


To learn about our research in elementary particle physics, 
visit the individual pages of our members.
<p>

Listed here are 
office numbers in 
the Barus & Holley building, phone extensions and email address at
<b> het.brown.edu</b>.
From off campus dial (401) 863-<i>extension</i>.

You can look up other people at Brown in the
University's
<a href="gopher://ns.brown.edu:105/2">
Online Directory.</a>

More address and e-mail info below.
(<a href="index-notables.html">Plain text version</a> available.)
