<TITLE> 
Physics Preprints
</TITLE>


<h1>
<img src="/images/info.gif">
Physics Preprints
</h1>

<p>
<hr>
<b>Server update</b>:  There is a new test interface on home page
for preprints
which will run TeX automatically with no intervention whatever and
store the file locally.  All later clicks will view the local copy.
Please try to break it and report any success.
<hr>
<p>

New research papers can be fetched automatically from the 
   <a href="http://mentor.lanl.gov:80/Welcome.html">
Los Alamos Physics Information Service.</A> 
(LANL is running a new test WWW server.  The 
   <a href="http://info.cern.ch/hypertext/DataSources/bySubject/Physics/LANL.html">
old interface</A>
is still available, though.)

To learn how to submit papers to the bulletin boards and how
to subscribe to daily e-mail distributions of abstracts, click 
   <a href="/guide/email-help.html">
here</A> 
or follow the links on LANL.
<p>

You may find the web even easier to browse than the daily e-mail listings:
here are links to July cumulative title/abstract listings on
   <a href="http://mentor.lanl.gov:80/hep-th/listings/9307.html">
hep-th</a>
and on
   <a href="http://mentor.lanl.gov:80/hep-ph/listings/9307.html">
hep-ph</a>
.
<p>
Bibliographic searches can be started from 
   <a href="http://slacvm.slac.stanford.edu./FIND/hep">
the SPIRES database at SLAC,</A> 
with hypertext links directly to papers sources from Los Alamos.
<p>

Locally, Mosaic has been hot-wired to 
   <a href="/guide/tex.html">
run TeX automatically. </A>
<P>



<H2>
On-Line Preprint Library
</H2>

To run the local on-line library, 
select <B>Physics E-prints</B> from the system
   <a href="/guide/menu.html">
<B>Information</B> </A>
menu.
This consists of papers someone else in the group thought were
interesting enough to at least browse.
It is not as complete as going through the LANL listings, but it
is much faster.
Double-click on the 
   <a href="/guide/eprints.html">
icons</A>
to change directories and to 
preview a paper.
<P>

[ <a href="/"> Back </a> to HET home page ]

