<HEAD>
<TITLE>HST News</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>

<H1>New HST camera: before/after, 13 January 1994</H1>

One of the very first images of the new 
Wide-Field and Planetary Camera-II,
compared with an earlier image (WFPC-I)  of the same region (M100 galaxy).

<HR>

<A href=http://cdsweb.u-strasbg.fr/wfpc.1.gif><img src="wfpc-01.gif"></A>

<HR>

The official announcement from NASA/JPL is 
<A href="wfpc-pix.html">here.
</A>
<href=ftp://jplinfo.jpl.nasa.gov/JPLPAO/PUBLIC/JPLINFO/news/wfpc-pix.pr>

<P>
<ADDRESS><A href=http://cdsweb.u-strasbg.fr/CDS.html>CDS, Strasbourg</A>
