   <H2> Research Interests </H2>

  Matrix Models, Lattice QCD.<p>

For a graph on my summer (1993) "work" follow <A HREF="cover.gif">this</A> and 
<A HREF="paros2.gif">this</A>. 1994 was a bad summer in Providence....
 
  <UL>

  <LI>  <a href="http://xxx.lanl.gov/find/hep-lat/1/orginos/0/2/0/all/1/0">
  Bulletin Board Papers</a>

