<p>

<h1>Matthew Parry</h1>
</center>
As you've no doubt worked out, I'm a graduate student in the
<a href="http://www.het.brown.edu"> High Energy Physics group</a>
 at
<a href="http://www.brown.edu"> Brown University</a>.
I am interested in cosmology, particularly theories of the early 
universe, and semi-classical physics. I also dabble in fluid dynamics, 
modelling of concepts in
<a href="http://robotics.jpl.nasa.gov/tasks/aerobot/homepage.html">  
planetary exploration</a>
and ideas of consciousness.
<p>

<hr>
<center><b>The obligatory some-of-my-favourite-links section</b></center>
<hr>
<p>
<ul>

<li>How to make <a href="http://nz.com/NZ/Culture/Food/PavRecipe.html">
pavlova</a> , New Zealand's national dessert.
<br>

<li>Information on
<a href="http://flyingnun.nz.com/Welcome.html">Flying Nun</a>
 , home of some truly great music.
<br>

<li>How to embarrass a multi-national. Do you want fries with that
<!a href="http://www.interlog.com/eye/Misc/McLibel/">
<a href="http://www.envirolink.org/mcspotlight/home.html">McLibel</a>
 ?
<br>

<li>Some thoughts on how and how not to
<a href="http://sunsite.unc.edu/wxyc/economy.ideas.html">copyright in the 
computer era</a>
 from John Perry Barlow.
<br>

<li>And on this subject, find out what evil EMI have done to
<a href="http://www.olga.net/closed.html">OLGA</a> -the Online Guitar
Archive.
<br> 

<li>Decide if you have
<a href="http://www.outbreak.org/cgi-unreg/dynaserve.exe/Ebola/index.html"> 
ebola</a>. <br>

<li>Learn a number of useful things about
<a href="http://nz.com/NZ/">New Zealand</a>.
<br>

<li>Lots of
<a href="http://www2.webbernet.net/~bob/international.html">soccer</a>
 and <a href="http://www.cricket.org:8004/">cricket</a>
 results from around the world.
<br>

<li>Even if it has now become commercial,
<a href="http://us.imdb.com/">the IMDb</a>
 is a good place to find movie info. And here's
<a href=http:/uk.imdb.com/">the UK mirror site.</a>
<br>

<li>Another
<a href="http://www.phys.unsw.edu.au/~mettw/"> Matthew Parry</a>
 (no relation as far as I know).
<br>

<li>My current favourite: the amusing
<a href="http://weber.u.washington.edu/%7Ejwalsh/sokal/">Sokal affair</a>.
</ul>
<img src="/images/new.gif">Ruin your friends's interesting stories; debunk
those <a href="http://urbanlegends.com/">urban legends</a>. 
