        function doClock() {
                window.setTimeout( "doClock()", 1000 );
                today = new Date();
                self.status = today.toString();
    }
</script>



<h1>
<img src="/images/nomoney.gif" width=110 height=84>
The Boston Area Physics Calendar
</h1>
The Boston Area Physics Calendar is compiled and sold by
<a href="http://www.tufts.edu/as/physics/">Tufts</a>
but mirrored here 
<a href="http://www.adbusters.org/adbusters/Corporate/absolut.html"
target="_blank">absolutely</a>
free of charge.

BAPC submissions and inquiries should be sent to
<a href="mailto:bapc@tuhepa.phy.tufts.edu">
bapc@tuhepa.phy.tufts.edu
</a>.
<p>
<p>
The correct URL for this page is 
<a href="http://www.het.brown.edu/seminars/bapc/">
http://www.het.brown.edu/seminars/bapc/
</a> [note the trailing slash].
<p>
<p>
<i>- webmaster@het.brown.edu</i>
