<TITLE>System menu</TITLE>
<H1>System menu</H1>

The top-level system menu
looks like this:
<P>
<img src="/images/menu.gif">
<P>
<P>

If it isn't already pinned (notice the
thumbtack in the upper left corner) you can pop it up
with the right mouse button anywhere over the root window.
<P>
Hold down the right button to pop up the various submenus with
different programs and applications.
<P>
For example, the <B>Information</B> menu looks like this:
<P>
<img src="/images/menu-info.gif">
<P>
When you get to the application you want, just let go.

<p>

