<TITLE>On-line library</TITLE>
<H1>On-line library</H1>

The top-level Filemanager display for the on-line library
looks like this:
<P>
<img src="/images/filemgr.gif">
<P>
<P>

<B>Double-click</B> on one of the icons with the left mouse button
to open a directory,
<P>
<P>

<img src="/images/filemgr2.gif">
<P>
<P>
and then again to preview a paper or figure.
This is where papers are automatically filed after they have
been fetched and TeX'ed using xmosaic.
<P>

To print a paper, use the pop-up menu with the right mouse button.
Papers whose icons have a heavy black border have already
been printed once.  Please make a photocopy instead from
the copies next to the 5N library.

<p>
